@startuml REQ-0012 Sensor Calibration
autonumber

box "System" #LightBlue
  participant "Sensor Driver" as Sensor_Driver
end box

header
  **REQ-0012: Sensor Calibration**
  //Description:// Apply factory calibration offsets to sensor readings using data from the controller's calibration store.
  //Acceptance Criteria:// Sensor_Calibrate retrieves offsets via Controller_GetCalibration. Offsets applied to subsequent readings.
end header


Sensor_Driver -> Sensor_Driver: Controller_GetCalibration()

@enduml